Global Electronic Grade Citric Acid Market Insights
Electronic Grade Citric Acid Market size was valued at USD 0.72 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.12 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Electronic Grade Citric Acid Market Overview
The electronic grade citric acid market is estimated to reach a market value of USD 2.3 billion by 2027, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.5% during the forecast period. The increasing demand for high-purity citric acid in the production of electronics, specifically for cleaning and passivation processes in semiconductor manufacturing, is driving the market growth. Citric acid's role in improving the efficiency of electronic devices, along with its applications in cleaning agents, is contributing to its market expansion. Additionally, the growing demand for eco-friendly materials in electronic products supports the adoption of citric acid in electronic-grade formulations. This market is witnessing continuous innovations and advancements to cater to the rising demand for high-quality electronic-grade citric acid.

